# Ecommerce-server
This is the backend for the eCommerce platform built using Node.js, Express, and MongoDB.

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

Make sure you have the following installed:

  Node.js (v16 or higher)
  npm or Yarn
  MongoDB (locally or use MongoDB Atlas)

### Installation and Setup

1. **Clone the repository**:
     git clone https://github.com/sabithshass/Ecommerce-server.git
     cd Ecommerce-server

2. **Install Dependencies**:
   Using npm:npm install
   Using yarn:yarn install
  
3.**Run the Development Server**: 
   Using npm:npm start
   Using yarn:yarn dev

